condition.narrative: Completion of DA program in the Tirana Region by December 31, 2019.
Establishment of an inter-ministerial Coordination Working Group for decision making on implementation of reforms in socialassistance programs.

Finance Agreement: Appropriate budget allocations | Description: The Borrower shall ensure that, throughout the period of Projectimplementation, appropriate budget allocations' are made available yearly for Project implementation purposes. | Frequency: Yearly

Finance Agreement: Hire additional staff for MOLSA | Description: Within three (3) month from the effectiveness, the Borrower shallhave additional staff in the Department of Social Services Policy of MOLSA, with TOR acceptable to the Bank and with the projectmanagement, monitoring and evaluation expertise, and maintain thorough the project implementation period. | Due Date: 31-Jan-2013

Finance Agreement: Maintain the Project's Coordination Working Group | Description: Maintain, throughout the period of Projectimplementation, the Coordination Working Group, chaired by the Deputy Minister of MOLSA and including representatives from MOLSA,State Social Services and National Agency for Information Society, which is responsible for leading implementation of reforms insocial assistance programs and ensuring coordination of activities. | Frequency: Yearly
